Delhi
Aug 29, 2014
Child Sexual Abuse, Molestation
Description:
			A three-year-old girl was allegedly raped by her juvenile neighbour at the servant quarters near Jodhpur house in the heart of the national capital here this morning, police said.

The incident took place around 9 AM when the victim was playing outside her residence when the boy lured her to the room on some pretext and sexually assaulted her.

As the girl started crying, the locals informed police who rushed to the spot and apprehended the juvenile. The girl was sent for medical examination.

The juvenile accused was produced before the Juvenile Justice Board and sent to a correction home.